## Fix #15 queue (landed in R7)

- [x] **#15 Phase D carryover proration undercount.** R6c had 17 residual
  May shortfalls because per-partition ceil-proration across overlapping
  boundaries summed to less than the full-month gross target. Fix:
  cumulative-from-month-start proration so the last partition covering
  each month sees the full target. One-file math change in
  `preprocessing/rest_targets.py::compute_rest_targets` + 3-file plumbing
  (`partitioner.py` Partition fields, `checkpoint_manager.py` sub-partition
  forwarding, `model.py` kwargs). Backward-compat via Optional kwargs that
  fall back to per-partition bounds. **Verified R7b: 0 LC-06 shortfalls
  on full fleet.** 100% compliance for all 374 resources.

## Fix #14 queue (landed in R6)

